name: Our colorful world
description:
Everyone has a color

Every human being is born with a color,

And when it grows, it becomes one color, a thousand colors

Sometimes it takes on colors that don't even have a name

And you do not know what color it is

And how should you describe it?

People have the same color when they are small,

And whatever they take on, they still have the same color

But when they grow up,

Each of them has a color

For example, when they smile, they are blue

They are white when they walk

They are gray when they cry

They are red when they run

They turn yellow when they are sad

when ...

And every person in each state has a color different from other states and others

For example, my smile is blue

Your smile is orange

He has a red smile

And ...

The beauty of this world is its color

And the colorfulness of its people

You might say that a child's color is beautiful and an adult's color is ugly

But the best way is to think that being colorful is beautiful

Being colorful makes a difference,

And that difference makes sense to you, different senses

And we make friends based on the same colors,

These differences,

The same feelings

I make friends with someone whose smile is as blue as mine

Or not, I can even make friends with someone different from myself, someone whose smile is red or maybe yellow

 

We live with these colors

And good luck on earth!

And the beauty of this world is that you find the colors

You mean them

Understand them

Understand

Play with them

Think about them

Pay attention

And love them ...
